title: Sneaky LoL Themed Baby Names
body:
I am married, and for giggles wanted to pitch baby names to my wife, but instead of normal names, i want them to be league themed without her being able to guess. she has never played, nor does she want to and has no knowledge of the game aside from matches can take a really long time.

here are a few I  thought of:
Freelo
Maokai
Katarina
Orianna

more suggestions would be great. the funnier the better. I quite like Freelo atm
